fields.title: Shrek (2011)
fields.description: Shrek, an ogre, embarks on a journey with a donkey to rescue Princess Fiona from a vile lord and regain his swamp.

fields.description: When Shrek and Fiona return from their honeymoon, her parents, the rulers of Far Far Away, invite them over. But as the king does not like Shrek, he enlists a fairy to keep him away from his daughter.

fields.privacypolicy:
Privacy policy explains our practices, regarding the collection, use, and disclosure of certain information. This includes your personal information in connection with Cipherflix services.
Please visit our online help center if you have any questions or require any assistance regarding our services. When contacting us we will need to authenticate your identity, for your safety and ours before fulfilling your request. We receive and store information about you such as;

1) Information you provide us with: Name, Email address, Payment method, Telephone number, and other identifiers you might use.
2) Information about you when you use our services such as interaction with our customer service, when you rate us, account settings, and taste preference.
3) Information regarding your network, network devices, and other devices that you might use to access our services.
4) Information regarding your activity on Cipherflix such as title selection, shows you have watched, search queries, and a list of shows you might want to watch.

We protect this information according to our privacy policy, plus any additional restrictions imposed by the source of the data.
These sources could include: determining a location based on your IP address to customize our services with the help of services providers. Information to secure our systems, prevent fraud and help protect the security of Cipherflix account by our security service providers.
Information regarding payments, account balances, account updates based on their relationship with you by our payment service providers.
We use this information to provide, enhance and personalize, and administer our services, to process your registration, your payments, and to communicate with you on these services.
